init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: We were able to track the alien spaceship and we also know that Matt Damon is alive and well as he has been seen hanging out with the aliens.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The problem is that the aliens have put an invisibility shield around their ship so we cannot see it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I am going to build a rocket that will shoot a laser at the invisibility shield and knock it down.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Matt Damon, we have come to get you back on earth."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The shuttle launches into space and heads back towards earth.
